fields.description:
After updating the SDK to 5.1.2.GA, every <Button> inside a <ScrollableView> children view stops firing events. Tested on multiple environments using the same SDK version. 
Happens on both iOS 9.1 and 9.2.

Example:

{code:xml}
<Alloy>
	<Window>
		<ScrollableView id="content>
			<View>
				<Button onClick="test"/>
			</View>
		</ScrollableView>
	</Window>
</Alloy>
{code}


{code:javascript}
function test() {
    // this event is not triggered
    alert('testing');
}
{code}
